  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="AN196.1-kilavi">parattaiyiṟ pirintu vanta talaimakaṟkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">What SHE said to HIM who came [back] after having parted from the other woman.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AN196.1">
        <l>neṭuṅkoṭi nuṭaṅku naṟavumali pākkattu</l>
        <l>nāṭṭuṟaip paṭṭa mōṭṭiru varā<supplied>a</supplied>ṟ</l>
        <l>ṟuṭikkaṭ koḻuṅkuṟai noṭuttuṇ ṭāṭi</l>
        <l>vēṭṭa maṟantu tuñcuṅ koḻunaṟkup</l>
        <l>pāṭṭi yāmpalilai yamalaiveñ cōṟu</l>
        <l>tīmpuḷip pirampiṉ ṟiraḷkaṉi peytu</l>
        <l>viṭiyal vaikaṟai yiṭūu mūra</l>
        <l>toṭukalaṅ kuṟuka vāra ṟantai</l>
        <l>kaṇkavi ṉaḻinta kaṉappaṟ ṟeṟuvara</l>
        <l>voṉṟumoḻik kōcark koṉṟumuraṇ pōkiya</l>
        <l>kaṭuntērt titiyaṉ muntaik koḻuṅkuḻai</l>
        <l>yaṉṉi miñiliyi ṉiyalu</l>
        <l>niṉṉalat takuviyai muyaṅkiya mārpē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Oh man from a village, where at sunrise, at dawn</l>
        <l>the songstress puts hot rice in abundance on a waterlily leaf,</l>
        <l>pouring round fruits of sweet-sour Pirampu, (5-7)</l>
        <l>for [her] husband who sleeps, hunt forgotten, (4)</l>
        <l>having drunk [and] played after selling a fat piece with hourglass drum eyes (3)</l>
        <l>of Murrel fish big in the belly, that had turned up by the ghat [that] day, (2)</l>
        <l>in the village abounding in toddy where long banners sway, (1)</l>
        <l>don’t come to bring [it] close to the ornaments that touch [me], (8a-c)</l>
        <l>– [your] chest that has been embraced by your girl befitting in beauty, (13)</l>
        <l>who advances like Aṉṉi Miñili (12)</l>
        <l>with rich earrings [advanced] in front of Titiyaṉ with swift chariot, (11)</l>
        <l>whose enmity was gone after he had killed the Kōcar of one word, (10)</l>
        <l>so that many gold-pieces were scorched by which had perished</l>
        <l>the beauty of [his/her?] father’s eyes.(?) (8df.)</l>
      </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
